Japan Bank for International Cooperation/Japan: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback




























japan bank for international cooperation/japan
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Government
Industry: Government Development Banks
Sub-Industry: -
Japan Bank for International Cooperation. The Company provided international financial services to Japanese corporations. Main services included loans for exports & imports, overseas investment loans, untied loans, and loans to the overseas projects of Japanese corporations.




Corporate Information
Address:

Otemachi 1-4-1
Tokyo, 100-0004
Japan


