					Interviews
									







Project Financing for Natural Gas-fired Power Generation and Desalination Project : Interview with Deputy Director Kenichiro Kitamura and Deputy Director Hideaki Toyoda, Division 4, New Energy and Power Finance Department I, Infrastructure and Environment Finance Group 

Area: The Middle East Infrastructures[Project Finance] 








First Project Financing for the Republic of Trinidad and Tobago : Interview with Deputy Director Masahiro Ito, Division 1, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy and Natural Resources Finance Group 

Area: Latin America and the Caribbean Manufacturing and ServicesEnergy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Project Financing for the Shipping Business of Four LNG Tankers : Interview with then Deputy Director Hiroyuki Suzuki and Kana Koda, Division 1, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy and Natural Resources Finance Group 

Area: North America Marine and AerospaceEnergy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Supporting Expansion of Integrated Oil Refinery and Petrochemical Plant in Saudi Arabia : Interview with then Deputy Director Yoshihiro Uematsu, Yuma Kobayashi and Takumi Maekawa, Division 2, Corporate Finance Department, Industry Finance Group 

Area: The Middle East Manufacturing and Services[Project Finance] 








Strengthening Value-chain for Securing Stable Long-term LNG Supplies : Interview with Director Noriyasu Matsuda and Nana Suzuki, Division 1, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy and Natural Resources Finance Group 

Area: Oceania Marine and AerospaceEnergy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Project Financing for LNG Project in Indonesia : Interview with Deputy Director Satoshi Ikehara and Deputy Director Kojiro Nakao, Division 2, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy and Natural Resources Finance Group 

Area: Asia Energy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Project Financing an LNG Liquefaction Project in the U.S. : Interview with Director Noriyasu Matsuda and Deputy Director Hiroyuki Suzuki, Division 1, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy and Natural Resources Finance Group 

Area: North America Energy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Africa's First Ultra Super Critical Coal-Fired Power Plant in Morocco : Talking with Deputy Director Kenichiro Kitamura and Hiroshi Yasui of Division 3, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Africa Infrastructures[Project Finance] 








The Word's First Enhanced Oil (EOR) Recovery Project by Using CO2 Emissions from the Power Plant : Interview with Director Noriyasu Matsuda, Division 1, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy and Natural Resources Finance Group 

Area: North America EnvironmentEnergy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








First Project Financing for Offshore Wind Power Generation Project in UK : Talking with Director Kaoru Nagata and Saori Sone, Division 2, Nuclear and Renewable Energy Finance Department, Infrastructure and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Europe InfrastructuresEnvironment[Project Finance] 








JBIC-NEXI Facilities for STAR Oil Refinery Project in Turkey : Talking with Deputy Director Yoshihiro Uematsu and Yuuma Kobayashi, Division 2, Corporate Finance Department, Industry Finance Group 

Area: The Middle East Machinery and Equipment[Project Finance] 








First Project Financing for Hydro Power Plant Project in Lao People’s Democratic Republic (Lao PDR) : Talking with Deputy Director Ryoichi Abe and Michiko Hamada, Division 2, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Asia InfrastructuresEnvironment[Project Finance] 








Project Financing for Rajamandala Hydro Power Plant Project in Indonesia : Talking with Deputy Director Yuichiro Yoi and Kohei Sakashita, Division 2, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Asia InfrastructuresEnvironment[Project Finance] 








Project Financing for Sarulla Geothermal Power Plant Project in Indonesia : Talking with Yuichiro Yoi, Deputy Director, Division 2, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Asia InfrastructuresEnvironment[Project Finance] 








Project Financing for Kuwaitʼs First PPP Power and Seawater Desalination Project : Talking with Director Naoki Tamaki and Naoki Matsunaga, Division 3, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure Finance Group 

Area: The Middle East Infrastructures[Project Finance] 








Supporting the expansion of mine development project in Bolivia : Interview with Advisor Kuniyasu Kikuchi and Deputy Director Junsuke Arita, Division 1, Mining and Metals Finance Department, Energy, Natural Resources and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Latin America and the Caribbean Energy and Natural Resources 








Project Financing for Khanom 4 Gas-Fired Combined Cycle Power Plant in Thailand : Talking with Deputy Directors Masayuki Ota and Toshiyuki Takahashi, Division 2, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure Finance Group 

Area: Asia Infrastructures[Project Finance] 








Project Financing for Construction of an Oil Refinery and Petrochemical Complex in Vietnam : Talking with Yasushi Hirai, then Deputy Director, Division 2, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Natural Resources and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Asia Energy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Supporting Overseas Business Deployment of Japanese Company in Seawater Desalination Project : Talking with Daisuke Hamada, Deputy Director, Division 3, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure Finance Group 

Area: The Middle East InfrastructuresEnvironment[Project Finance] 








Supporting an Ultra-Deepwater FPSO Operation Project in Brazil : Talking with Director Katsuya Mogaki and Deputy Director Tomoyuki Miyaguchi Division 1, Marine and Aerospace Finance/Financial Products Department,  Industry Finance Group 

Area: Latin America and the Caribbean Marine and AerospaceEnergy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Project Financing for Deepwater FPSO Chartering Project for Offshore Oil Fields in Ghana : With Director Katsuya Mogaki Division 1, Marine and Aerospace Finance/Financial Products Department, Industry Finance Group 

Area: Africa Marine and AerospaceEnergy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Supporting the First Power Infrastructure Project by Japanese Company in Chile : With Deputy Director Yuichiro Yoi and Tomohiko Nishiu, Division 2, Power and Water Finance Department, Infrastructure Finance Group 

Area: Latin America and the Caribbean Infrastructures[Project Finance] 








Participating in One of the Largest Project Finance Deals to Date in International Financial Markets : With Deputy Director Yujin Numata, Division 1 of Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy, Natural Resources and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Oceania Energy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








Supporting the Development of Energy Artery on the Sea Linking Japan and Australia : With Director Soichiro Yamashita, Unit 3, Oil and Gas Finance Department, Energy, Natural Resources and Environment Finance Group 

Area: Oceania Marine and AerospaceEnergy and Natural Resources[Project Finance] 








To Improve Japanese Competitiveness in the Clean Energy Sector : With Director Kaoru Nagata, Deputy Director Kazunori Fukusumi, Osamu Matsumoto and Saori Sone, Unit 2, Nuclear and Renewable Energy Finance Department, Energy, Natural Resources and Environment Finance Group 

Area: North America InfrastructuresEnvironment[Project Finance] 








